TITLE: Installing Crossplane from Stable Channel Using Helm
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to install Crossplane from the stable Helm chart repository into a Kubernetes cluster. It ensures that the necessary namespace is created and the Helm repository is properly added and updated.
SOURCE: https://github.com/crossplane/crossplane/blob/main/cluster/charts/crossplane/README.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: console
CODE:
```
kubectl create namespace crossplane-system

helm repo add crossplane-stable https://charts.crossplane.io/stable
helm repo update

helm install crossplane --namespace crossplane-system crossplane-stable/crossplane
```

