TITLE: Defining MySQLInstanceRequirement in Crossplane YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet defines a MySQLInstanceRequirement custom resource in Crossplane. It specifies the requirements for a MySQL instance, including engine version, storage, and region. It also includes fields for resource binding and composition selection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/crossplane/crossplane/blob/main/design/design-doc-composition.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
apiVersion: database.example.org/v1alpha1
kind: MySQLInstanceRequirement
metadata:
  namespace: default
  name: sql
spec:
  engineVersion: "5.7"
  storageGB: 10
  region: us-west
  resourceRef:
  - name: default-sql-dd02m
  compositionSelector:
   matchLabels:
     connectivity: private
  compositionRef:
  - name: private-mysql-server
  writeConnectionSecretToRef:
    name: sql
```

