TITLE: Defining ImageConfig API for Crossplane Package Management in YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet defines the structure of the proposed ImageConfig API for Crossplane packages. It includes fields for matching images, registry configuration (authentication and TLS), and image verification settings using Cosign.
