TITLE: Configuring Change Logs via DeploymentRuntimeConfig in Crossplane
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration that enables change logging for a Crossplane provider by setting up a sidecar container, shared volume mount, and feature flag. This configuration can be reused across multiple providers.
