TITLE: Defining Provider API Object with Embedded Struct in Go
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the structure of a provider API object with an embedded struct containing both configurable and non-configurable fields. It serves as an example of how provider APIs may represent resources with mixed field types.
