TITLE: Defining Crossplane Browse ClusterRole in YAML
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet defines the 'crossplane-browse' ClusterRole, which allows read-only access to composite resources and compositions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/crossplane/crossplane/blob/main/design/design-doc-rbac-manager.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
